snippet.title: CloudBerry Kingdom - Dev Diary [UK]
snippet.description: Unhappily ever after. That's how it starts. The Orb resurfaces and the classic characters return. Kobbler with his mania, Princess with her endless boredom. It's only a matter of time before Bob, our hero, shows up to put order back to madness.
